data.description: MUST SEE.  2 bedroom, 1 bathroom home with 2 parking spots in the back of the home.  Main level has a large kitchen, dining space, living room, and an area for an office.  The kitchen has a rear door that goes out to the deck and the backyard.  The backyard is fenced in.  The upper level has 2 large bedrooms and a bathroom.  The home is move-in ready.  Freshly touched up with paint.  Roof is under 11 years old.  Don't miss out on this great home!
